Gg_fountain
------------
Four separate dust style buildings, gloomy hallways run in each.
Multiple ways to the rooftops.
32 Spawns.
Env_light matches theme of map.
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/75684
------------
Please comment/DL/ and assess.
Please do not edit/include in packs without permission.


gg_fountain_v2
-------------
Added 3D Skybox.
Added env_cubemaps.
Added env_sun.
Changed light_env colour.
Changed Coins on edges of building to func_illusionary.
Added sufficient lighting to hallways.
Removed some fence posts.
Fixed minor texture errors.
-------------

SGT_kick_ur_ass for his Sun tut.
Nosoul and The BucKeT for their feedback.
